<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="virtual-horses">Virtual Horses</h3>
<h4 id="the-game">The game</h4>
<p>This is a virtual horse racing game that allows you to place real money bets on the result of virtual horse races. A Play for Fun version of the game is not available.</p>
<p>All players playing the game at the same time, see the same races and the same results, wherever they are. All race simulations are created through a combination of Artificial Intelligence and independent random number generators.</p>
<h4 id="race-events-and-races">Race events and races</h4>
<p>Race events are shown continuously. A new race event will start as soon as the current one has finished. Each event has 6 participants. A race has a total duration of approximately 120 seconds.</p>
