<h4 id="betting">Betting</h4>
<p>Betting is allowed up to 10 seconds prior to the race start. Betting options for future races of the current race days remain open. You can select any bet option for all available matches. Click on the odds relating to bet you wish to place. See (4) in the image above.</p>
<p>The following race betting options are available:</p>
<ol>
<li><p><strong>Win</strong> – bet on the selected horse to win the race (e.g., Horse No.1 finishes 1st).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Place</strong>(1-2) – bet on the selected horse to finish 1st or 2nd position in a race. (e.g., Selection 1: Horse No.1 finishes 1st or 2nd)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Show</strong>(1-3) – bet on the selected horse to finish 1st, 2nd or 3rd position in the race (e.g., Selection 1: Horse No.1 finishes 1st, 2nd or 3rd).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Even/Odd</strong> – bet on horse No.Even (2/4/6) or horse No.Odd (1/3/5) as winner.</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Over/Under</strong> – bet on the winner horse is over or under No.3.5 (Selection Over: Horse No.4/No.5/No.6 finishes 1st; Selection Under: Horse No.1/No.2/No.3 finishes 1st).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Exacta</strong> – bet on the 2 horses finishing in 1st and 2nd positions, in the order predicted. Both predictions must be correct for the bet to win. (e.g., Selection 1, 2: Horse No.1 finishes 1st, Horse No.2 finishes 2nd)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Quinella</strong> – bet on the 2 horses you expect to finish 1st and 2nd in any order. Both predictions must be correct for the best to win. (e.g., Selection1&amp;2: Horses No.1 and No.2 finish 1st and 2nd in any order)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Trifecta</strong> – bet on the 3 horses you expect to finish 1st, 2nd and 3rd in the correct order. All three predictions must be correct for the bet to win. (e.g., Selection 1, 2, 3: Horse No.1 finishes 1st, Horse No.2 finishes 2nd, Horse No.3 finishes 3rd)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="your-bets">Your bets</h4>
<p>As you make your bet selections by clicking on the odds relating to the bet you wish to place, the betslip will open. Once you have made all your selections, enter your stake in the betslip Stake field and click on Bet. Your bet will be placed.</p>
<p>Virtual Horse Racing bets cannot be combined in the same betslip with bets placed on real sport events.</p>
<p>If your bet is successful, your winnings will automatically be credited to your account.</p>
<p>To see the list of your Virtual Horses bets, please go to Virtuals page and click on &quot;MY BETS&quot; next &quot;BETSLIP&quot;. You will find a list of all bets you have placed. Also you can find details in the &quot;Bets History&quot; in the bottom of &quot;MY BETS&quot;.</p>
